assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  通常染埋頭皮就唔好"},{"pid":"b2b069a5ebac355966638caea1fdf657e4ea811f","tid":146033,"uid":86575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 小弟我就放緊Study Leave 想話唔使再返學 去染個髮 順便染走啲白髮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我想染深啡或者灰呢啲低調色 但聽人講話啲頭髮無漂過係好難上色 甚至根本同無染一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想問而家應該點做好 去萬寧到買啲cheap cheap染髮劑好定正正經經去salon漂染好 我係想見到同黑髮有明顯分別既效果 但不竟我都唔係話想用太貴 補習都用左我唔少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係染髮劑推薦邊一隻 如果係去salon漂染又去邊間好 同埋幾錢到?</blockquote><br />\n岩岩先睇到<span style=\"color: red;\">灰呢啲低調色</span> 其實唔低調 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o90s8q6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo90s8q6.jpg&h=a3ac2596&s={SIZE}\" />灰色你拎定五百以上 八百以下 出黎啦"},{"pid":"845fd2983e89ecaa18c775b5e753de768e8f505d","tid":146033,"uid":49772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"旺角樓上鋪<br />\n漂一次300<br />\n染一次兩舊<br />\n之前染過啞灰色<br />\n要漂兩次<br />\n<br />\n俾你參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 灰色好快甩 唔好搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋漂過一次好難返轉頭"},{"pid":"de5a5b328742ff6c2d7014759d1cd67d538ea3c8","tid":146033,"uid":13704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb7c02cbc1b0b95024f5f5c96672145543e4aecc","tid":146033,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"勸你過埋畢業禮先好染<br />\n唔係搵自己搞"},{"pid":"fa6909faca21430a3a0915b9610221e26be65b23","tid":146033,"uid":50290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:25